Michele B. Chan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michele_B._Chan 0 Michele B. Chan is an American philanthropist and former actress. She is best known as for roles as Dr. Donna Chen on the Canadian series, Danger Bay, and as Mei Jan on the ABC television, MacGyver, during the 1980s.
